  "name": "RPlog_Swoop_Racing_with_Selektah",
  "title": "A Dead Heat at Hideaway Beach",
  "summary": "On the sands of Hideaway Beach near Plaxton City, the racer Piper Drake pulls up on her swoop Terminal Velocity to challenge Selektah, who lounges against his Black Axiom swoop Agony. The two confident pilots banter briefly before lining up for an impromptu race along a treacherous beachfront course of straightaways, dunes, thick brush, and crashing waves. Trading the lead repeatedly through each leg, they prove evenly matched, with Piper surprised to find Selektah a far tougher opponent than expected. Both opt for the shorter, more dangerous final path over the rocks and breaking water, and cross the finish line in a dead-even tie. Impressed with one another, they share a respectful handshake, exchange friendly promises of a rematch on the real track, and part ways.",
